{"article_id":"GMGGdAkZAsnjxzvw","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Massachusetts Democratic Sen. Elizabeth Warren on Sunday ruled out a 2020 presidential run and taking a DNA test","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"to prove Native American ancestry","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"-- an issue","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"that has nagged her Senate campaigns","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"and would almost certainly create problems in a White House bid .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"\" I ' m not running for president , \"","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"Warren , a champion of the Democratic Party ' s progressive wing , told \" Fox News Sunday . \"","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"When asked Sunday","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"whether she ' d agree to calls for genetic testing","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"to resolve the heritage controversy ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"Warren launched into a family history ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"as purportedly told by her parents and grandparents ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"before saying ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"\" It ' s a part of who I am ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"and no one ' s ever going to take that away . \"","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"Warren ,","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"who is seeking a second Senate term this year ,","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"has been accused of saying","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"she is of Native American heritage","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"to help in securing jobs ,","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"including one as a Harvard law professor .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"She has acknowledged identifying as a minority ,","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"but denies using such status","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"to help advance her career .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"President Trump has repeatedly called Warren , a Wall Street critic and potential White House rival , \" Pocahontas , \" a notable American Indian woman in colonial history ,","depth":3},{"id":25,"text":"to highlight the controversy .","depth":3},{"id":26,"text":"\" Let me tell you a little bit about my family , \"","depth":3},{"id":27,"text":"Warren said Sunday .","depth":3},{"id":28,"text":"\" My mom and dad were born and raised out in Oklahoma ,","depth":3},{"id":29,"text":"and my daddy was in his teens","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"when he fell in love with my mother .","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"\" She was a beautiful girl","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"who played the piano .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"And he was head over heels in love with her","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"and wanted to marry her .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"And his family was bitterly opposed to that","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"because she was part Native American . \" And eventually my parents eloped","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"and they survived the Great Depression ,","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"they survived The Dust Bowl .","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"They went through a lot of hard times .","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"They raised three boys , my older brothers ,","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"all of whom went off to the military . `` They raised me .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"They knocked around","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"and it was tough","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"but they hung together .","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"They hung together for 63 years .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"I know","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"who I am","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"because of what my mother and my father told me , what my grandmother and my grandfather told me , what all my aunts and uncles told me and my brothers . \"","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":97,"left":74,"right":96,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":72,"right":73,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":63,"right":71,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":63,"left":55,"right":62,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":55,"left":53,"right":54,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":53,"left":50,"rig